value: The two explored a dark labyrinth.\nIn the depths, they found a lever...
A trap! They muscled their way out...\nThank goodness they had each other!
A trap! They artfully evade danger.\nThe labyrinth is theirs before long!
Trapped! ...And having fun with it!\nThey played to their heart's content.
$aFoes grant 5x SP for the next $a0,\nand then 2x SP thereafter! (Only highest\nvalue applied. Does not stack.)
